{"tid":1975041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(估國家)New Balance吿New Barlun侵權 獲賠1188萬","createTime":"2020-04-16T09:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T09:59:26.000Z","uid":251052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef72d14df19e23edc62a055efed415579d60369","tid":1975041,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200416&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60837620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200416%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60837620&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10MsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e4fc0bc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200416%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60837620&h=2b0459af\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200416&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60837620</a><br />\n<br />\n內地山寨品牌無數，有時甚至連正牌反被山寨告。美國著名運動品牌「New Balance」歷盡萬難，終於獲得平反。上海市浦東新區人民法院今日對「New Balance」及內地「NEW&middot;BARLUN」的商標糾紛案件作出判決。<br />\n<br />\n判決指出，「NEW&middot;BARLUN」品牌方紐巴倫（中國）有限公司停止對「New Balance」品牌方新百倫貿易（中國）有限公司的不正當競爭行為，並發公開聲明消除影響，賠償經濟損失1,000萬元人民幣（下同‧約1,100萬港元）及維權合理開支80萬元（約88萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n「New Balance」運動鞋在中國具極高知名度和市場佔有率，其所屬新平衡體育運動公司是美國著名的運動製品生產商。該公司先後在中國商標局註冊「New Balance」、「NB」、「N」字母等系列商標。「New Balance」運動鞋有一項標誌性設計，即在鞋兩側中央位置靠近鞋帶處使用大寫的英文字母「N」裝潢。<br />\n<br />\n原告認為，被告紐巴倫公司大量生產、銷售兩側印有「N」字樣的運動鞋，侵犯了新平衡體育運動公司的商品裝潢。被告持續實施不正當競爭行為，導致原告產品評價降低，商譽貶損，給原告帶來巨大損失。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\nApp內1-Click訂閱《蘋果動新聞》<br />\n按此了解更多 <br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n【78頁電子書●你不能不知的毛澤東】<br />\n老毛秘史和他的女人們 熟讀紅色抗爭策略<br />\n一按即睇︰ <a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/e/fJX5EvX1v2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2Fe%2FfJX5EvX1v2&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10MsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=3122be42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/e/fJX5EvX1v2</a>"},{"pid":"9e6444a039aabce2e49a099991665561f89af43b","tid":1975041,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"呢d post就唔會有人推"},{"pid":"9638fc8f9b30dba812b024cc2d9085aaecac7b4c","tid":1975041,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"終於贏<br />\n之後會唔會有一大堆跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeedb69d052c19c95bf91951606e705f18111a17","tid":1975041,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9638fc8f9b30dba812b024cc2d9085aaecac7b4c","tid":1975041,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"終於贏<br />\n之後會唔會有一大堆跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"jordan都贏左"},{"pid":"557ce61c8ddb5c37745e6b444c9f151909b2b37a","tid":1975041,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"美國同支那之前有講過數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5cde9c626d74e4c3c4f39d439faf1cd4dca173","tid":1975041,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"撩巴撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2b5163843b020db923de891dbda39923460a43","tid":1975041,"uid":331421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"證明中共依家真係好驚外資撤離中國"},{"pid":"a52ee0bd4c2090fd1256ccd41fc7cc86252b2e71","tid":1975041,"uid":342527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"燒生好似估中左<br />\n佢講過美國牌子開始會贏侵權案"},{"pid":"987d01d563eebcc0307e0a32c7d7e1f03d2ba0bf","tid":1975041,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"好多外資停左訂單，支那立刻搞小動作"},{"pid":"5533fc3d9cb109e1c26c9a2d5e0cfade4d70ccdb","tid":1975